    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Mar 29, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-29/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Mar 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-29/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Lawsuit claims hackers stole customer data at 1000 Arby&amp;rsquo;s stores&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Arby&amp;rsquo;s knew the danger of not safeguarding its POS network as various high profile data breaches have occurred in the same way, including data &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://registerguard.com/rg/business/35422976-63/lawsuit-claims-hackers-stole-customer-data-at-1000-arbys-stores.html.csp&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://registerguard.com/rg/business/35422976-63/lawsuit-claims-hackers-stole-customer-data-at-1000-arbys-stores.html.csp&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;XenData&amp;rsquo;s New Multi-Tier Storage Platform Certified for Axxon Intellect&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Broadcasting &amp;amp; Cable &amp;hellip; storage systems are certified platforms for AxxonSoft&amp;rsquo;s cutting-edge Intellect Enterprise physical security information management (PSIM) software.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.broadcastingcable.com/thewire/xendata-s-new-multi-tier-storage-platform-certified-axxon-intellect-enterprise-software/164460&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.broadcastingcable.com/thewire/xendata-s-new-multi-tier-storage-platform-certified-axxon-intellect-enterprise-software/164460&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Internet subscriptions fall further in Nigeria&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Users are increasingly aware of privacy and security issues in general, and specifically in relation to data breaches. The number of reported data &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://guardian.ng/business-services/internet-subscriptions-fall-further-in-nigeria/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://guardian.ng/business-services/internet-subscriptions-fall-further-in-nigeria/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Relatively new Melbourne reseller signs deal with CrowdStrike&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The CrowdStrike Falcon Platform unifies antivirus, endpoint detection and response (EDR) and a &lt;sup&gt;24&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;frasl;&lt;sub&gt;7&lt;/sub&gt; managed threat hunting, all via a single &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://channellife.com.au/story/relatively-new-melbourne-reseller-signs-deal-crowdstrike/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://channellife.com.au/story/relatively-new-melbourne-reseller-signs-deal-crowdstrike/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;neXgen and Vidsys enhance smart city security and safety&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;neXgen Group, a smart city advisory and managed services provider, is to offer Vidsys Smart Safety and Security as a service leveraging a converged &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://smartcitiesworld.net/news/nexgen-and-vidsys-enhance-smart-city-security-and-safety-1527&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://smartcitiesworld.net/news/nexgen-and-vidsys-enhance-smart-city-security-and-safety-1527&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;If You Want to Stop Big Data Breaches, Start With Databases&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over the past few years, large-scale data breaches have become so common that even tens of millions of records leaking feels unremarkable.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.wired.com/2017/03/want-stop-big-data-breaches-start-databases/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.wired.com/2017/03/want-stop-big-data-breaches-start-databases/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How to fend off cyberattacks and data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experts in online security and data protection explain how smaller businesses can prevent security breaches and digital attacks.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cio.com/article/3186269/cyber-attacks-espionage/how-to-fend-off-cyberattacks-and-data-breaches.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.cio.com/article/3186269/cyber-attacks-espionage/how-to-fend-off-cyberattacks-and-data-breaches.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Thai businesses at risk of data breaches: study&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thai businesses may be at risk of data breaches, as almost one in 3 Thais (29.5 per cent) are using unapproved personal devices for work, according &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://tech.thaivisa.com/thai-businesses-at-risk-of-data-breaches-study-2/20672/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://tech.thaivisa.com/thai-businesses-at-risk-of-data-breaches-study-2/20672/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;XOR Data Exchange Releases Fraud Prevention Tool For Online Retailers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Online retailers will know if and how many times a consumer has experienced data breaches and whether these breaches have led to any fraud.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pymnts.com/whats-hot-2/2017/xor-data-exchange-releases-fraud-prevention-tool-for-online-retailers/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.pymnts.com/whats-hot-2/2017/xor-data-exchange-releases-fraud-prevention-tool-for-online-retailers/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Content tracking, analytics hold the key to endpoint data protection&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Faith: The small data breaches are way more likely to happen. For example, the Secret Service agent&amp;rsquo;s stolen laptop that was recently in the news had &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://searchenterprisedesktop.techtarget.com/news/450415809/Content-tracking-analytics-hold-the-key-to-endpoint-data-protection&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://searchenterprisedesktop.techtarget.com/news/450415809/Content-tracking-analytics-hold-the-key-to-endpoint-data-protection&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;CylancePROTECT Selected by SANS Community as Best Endpoint Protection&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Finance Cylance Inc., the company that revolutionized traditional antivirus with AI-powered prevention that blocks everyday malware along with today&amp;rsquo;s most &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/cylanceprotect-selected-sans-community-best-140000968.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/cylanceprotect-selected-sans-community-best-140000968.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cloud Distribution Ltd - Cloud Distribution Advances Security Portfolio&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MENAFN.COM &amp;hellip; new standard in endpoint security by being the first and only platform to unify next-generation antivirus (AV), endpoint detection and response (EDR) &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://menafn.com/1095354112/Cloud-Distribution-Ltd-%7C-Cloud-Distribution-Advances-Security-Portfolio-with-Endpoint-Protection-Leader-CrowdStrike&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://menafn.com/1095354112/Cloud-Distribution-Ltd-%7C-Cloud-Distribution-Advances-Security-Portfolio-with-Endpoint-Protection-Leader-CrowdStrike&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Businesses lose 44 data records every second&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The US is a &amp;ldquo;clear leader&amp;rdquo; when it comes to the number of data breaches occurring every year (1,348), with the UK being second. That being said, the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://betanews.com/2017/03/29/businesses-lose-44-data-records-every-second/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://betanews.com/2017/03/29/businesses-lose-44-data-records-every-second/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;In wake of EMV switch, US e-commerce fraud soars&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experian says that the biggest component of credit card fraud trends is the fact that 2016 was a record year for data breaches. There were 1,093 &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.finextra.com/newsarticle/30358/in-wake-of-emv-switch-us-e-commerce-fraud-soars/retail&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.finextra.com/newsarticle/30358/in-wake-of-emv-switch-us-e-commerce-fraud-soars/retail&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
